comments: Barnes (TOR) commits a take foul on Cunningham (DET) by grabbing his jersey.
Anunoby (TOR) makes contact to Grant's (DET) body that affects his SQBR.
Hayes (DET) reaches in and makes contact to Dragic's (TOR) arm, causing him to lose control of the ball.
Anunoby (TOR) makes marginal contact with Cunningham's (DET) body that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Grant (DET) establishes himself in a legal guarding position in Siakam's (TOR) path during the drive to the basket and Siakam dislodges him from that position.
Anunoby (TOR) reaches in as Cunningham (DET) loses control of the ball and any contact is marginal.
Siakam (TOR) reaches in and makes contact with the ball, but Stewart (DET) touches it last before it goes out of bounds.  The Raptors should be given possession of the ball.
Anunoby (TOR) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Bey (DET) and the ensuing contact is incidental.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests Stewart's (DET) post shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Grant (DET) makes marginal body contact with Barnes (TOR) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Dragic (TOR) releases the pass before stepping out of bounds.
Stewart (DET) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact while contesting Barnes' (TOR) shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Bey (DET).
Dragic (TOR) trips Bey (DET) and causes him to lose his balance.
